{"tid":1394704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國家主席有野同大家講","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:34:40.000Z","uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8292198924a9e5338be574ea2c8bafae713414b9","tid":1394704,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"近日黃屍暴徒有破壞無建設，淨係識衝擊法治，破壞香港繁榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />偉大既毛黨主席點教你地架，你地班黃屍同我睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬克思主義的道理千條萬續，歸根結底就是一句話，造反有理！<br />\n<br />\n用革命的兩手，對待反革命的兩手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打得贏就打，打不贏就走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哪裡有壓迫，哪裡就有反抗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷史是人民創造的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n槍桿子里面出政權！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BEeDHNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBEeDHNN.png&h=591c9349&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsf7A7O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdsf7A7O.png&h=b7c72a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL4wik8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL4wik8.png&h=9ff2b790&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}